{"tid":578642,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"識唔識人平時會用自己個名嚟叫自己，而唔係用「我」","createTime":"2018-03-02T19:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T07:53:29.000Z","uid":23094,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e6ac0cf1b287778b1ae12587768d4e2bee1b2e47","tid":578642,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T19:54:28.000Z","msg":"成日睇動畫都總會有一兩個角色會咁，多數係女角色<br />\n通常都係用返身邊啲人稱呼自己嗰個名嚟稱呼返自己<br />\n<br />\n但係現實有冇人真係會咁？<br />\n我就好似未見過<br />\n係咪日本先有？<br />\n<br />\n同埋日本人自己一個食飯嗰陣係咪都會講<br />\n「我唔客氣喇」同「多謝款待」？<br />\n<br />\n有冇日本巴打解答到"},{"pid":"dcc7ac58bd95a5ae82107c20527edd77c5b3f2f5","tid":578642,"uid":26675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T19:59:56.000Z","msg":"識<br />\n-完-"},{"pid":"f0794047a993f5af09fb17c6bf3de9845b864f18","tid":578642,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T20:07:17.000Z","msg":"庶"},{"pid":"a8dd46bf4735c958f5c95ed8a5e59174c8c60a82","tid":578642,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T20:13:13.000Z","msg":"朕"},{"pid":"14668160ef2bd643429ea8e2bcfe317799787d42","tid":578642,"uid":59465,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T20:15:49.000Z","msg":"扮可愛嘅人先會咁"},{"pid":"905d778d664956dfbb071448f6fd4c69a3013b37","tid":578642,"uid":44073,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T20:18:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04f336e308462a737d4c04d799e2a97fb54c1070","tid":578642,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T20:29:16.000Z","msg":"卡卡西會"},{"pid":"ddf35e746e5ca2c7d831ac00bcee7634c1974094","tid":578642,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T21:38:40.000Z","msg":"同埋日本人自己一個食飯嗰陣係咪都會講<br />\n「我唔客氣喇」同「多謝款待」？<br />\n<br />\n唔會"},{"pid":"bbefa1a743be14f7296f25a2fea371080c4fe1c4","tid":578642,"uid":97970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T00:50:17.000Z","msg":"俺